Injector/Bumblebee/Double Punch:


Injector dived, the electrical bolt missing, chasing TK, he fired off two 
stinger missiles at the the middle of TK's back, only 30 ft behind him, 
laughing as he sees Double Punch's missile chasing on him, gaining quickly.

Double Punch fired off two missiles at the rock Megatron was behind.

---

Bumblebee's scanners could detect Megatron, who was 40 meters away.  It was 
only a matter of time.
